{% extends "en-base.twig" %}

{% block content %}
	<style>
		@media(max-width: 767px) {
			.hero-mobile {
				margin-bottom: -99px !important;
				right: -45px;
			}
		}

		@media(min-width: 768px) {
			section.banner .banner-hero .hero-img {
				right: -184px;
				bottom: -94px;
			}
		}

		@media(min-width: 992px) {
			section.banner .banner-hero .hero-img {
				right: -263px;
				bottom: -131px;
			}
		}
		@media(min-width: 1440px) {
			section.banner .banner-hero .hero-img {
				bottom: -129px;
			}
		}
	</style>
	<!-- Banner -->
	<section class="banner form-space">
		<div class="container banner-hero two-lines">
			<div class="banner-hero-cont">
				<h1 class="form-hide">Grow super-fast
					<br class="d-block d-md-none">with exceptional
					<br class="d-block d-md-none">Shopify SEO</h1>
				<div class="banner-description">
					<p class="form-hide"></p>
					<div class="form-hide hero-mobile">
						<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo_mob.png" srcset="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo_mob.png, {{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo_mob@2x.png 2x" alt="First Page"/>
					</div>
				</div>
				{% include "partials/en-form-services.twig" with {'form_page': 'Shopify SEO', 'form_button': 'Get A Free Quote'} %}
				{% include "partials/en-section-awards-badges.twig" %}
			</div>
			<div class="hero-img d-none d-md-block d-lg-none">
				<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo_tab.png" srcset="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo_tab.png, {{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo_tab@2x.png 2x" alt="First Page"/>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-img d-none d-lg-block">
				<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo.png" srcset="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo.png, {{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_hero_seo@2x.png 2x" alt="First Page"/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{% include "partials/en-section-featured-in-news.twig" %}

	<section class="section-paragraph section-white mob-center">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row mb-3 mb-md-5 flex-column-reverse flex-md-row flex-md-row-reverse align-items-center">
				<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mt-3 mb-3 text-center text-lg-right">
					<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/shopify-growth.png" srcset="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/shopify-growth@2x.png 2x" class="img-fluid d-none d-md-inline-block" alt="Skyrocket traffic & sales with Shopify SEO"/>

					<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/shopify-growth-mb.png" srcset="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/shopify-growth-mb@2x.png 2x" class="img-fluid d-md-none" alt="Skyrocket traffic & sales with Shopify SEO"/>

				</div>
				<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-3">
					<h2>Skyrocket traffic & sales with Shopify SEO</h2>
					<p>Shopify has proven to be an incredible resource for budding e-commerce brands looking to attract and convert customers. Powered by a remarkably user-friendly design, it doesn’t take a lot of technical know-how to upload your products and start shipping to customers. However, it’s no use having an online store if your customers aren't aware of it. This is why a robust Shopify SEO campaign has become an essential part of running an e-commerce platform.</p>
					<p>The world of e-commerce gets more competitive every day as more businesses fight for attention. If you’re looking to stay ahead of the game, First Page Australia’s talented digital marketers know how to attract your customers and outperform your rivals. Across detailed on-page and technical
						<a href="{{ home_url }}seo/">SEO</a>
						strategies, we have the power to skyrocket your Shopify store’s leads and traffic.</p>
					<div class="button-cont">
						<button type="button" class="btn fp-btn fp-btn-orange show-popup-form">GET A FREE SEO QUOTE</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row mb-3 mb-md-5 align-items-center flex-column-reverse flex-md-row">
				<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mt-3 mb-3 text-center">
					<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_seo_we_dont_outsource_pc.png" srcset="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_seo_we_dont_outsource_pc@2x.png 2x" class="img-fluid d-none d-md-inline-block" alt="Optimise your e-commerce platform"/>

					<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_seo_we_dont_outsource_mb.png" srcset="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_seo_we_dont_outsource_mb@2x.png 2x" class="img-fluid d-md-none" alt="Optimise your e-commerce platform"/>

				</div>
				<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-3">
					<h2>Optimise your e-commerce platform</h2>
					<p>Australia is one of Shopify’s fastest-growing regions, with 10,000 local businesses already capitalising on the platform. Much of its rapid adoption can be attributed to its highly customisable nature, with brands of all shapes and sizes managing an online store that reflects their needs. Meanwhile, Shopify’s streamlined backend comes pre-loaded with a range of basic SEO functions to assist in attracting the right customers.</p>
					<p>But if your business is truly going to stride ahead in the growing e-commerce marketplace, you’re going to need some expert help. With global online sales expected to top USD $5 billion in 2021, planning and executing a highly optimised Shopify store could be the difference-maker between success and failure. With the help of our talented team, your brand will continue to prosper long into the future.</p>
					<div class="button-cont">
						<button type="button" class="btn fp-btn fp-btn-orange show-popup-form">GET A FREE SEO QUOTE</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row mb-3 mb-md-5 align-items-center flex-column-reverse flex-md-row flex-md-row-reverse">
				<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mt-3 mb-3 text-center text-lg-right">
					<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_business_success.svg" class="img-fluid d-none d-md-inline-block" alt="Surpass your sales aspirations"/>

					<img src="{{ site.theme.link }}/assets/img/img_business_success_mb.svg" class="img-fluid d-md-none" alt="Surpass your sales aspirations"/>

				</div>
				<div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-3">
					<h2>Surpass your sales aspirations</h2>
					<p>Part of what makes Shopify so incredible is the platform’s built-in analytical features. This provides compelling data on customer trends, site movements and conversion rates. Yet many business owners don’t have the necessary experience to implement changes based on this information. Join hundreds of other e-commerce brands and partner with First Page Australia – we know exactly how to make sense of these figures to lead an effective SEO campaign.</p>
					<p>While it’s possible to make do with Shopify’s straightforward SEO tools, if you’re ready to take your business to the next level, it requires an involved and highly technical approach. Through a productive backlink profile, canonical URLs, and the coordination of Shopify SEO with Google Analytics, our talented team will skyrocket your e-commerce brand’s visibility.</p>
					<div class="button-cont">
						<button type="button" class="btn fp-btn fp-btn-orange show-popup-form">GET A FREE SEO QUOTE</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>


	{% include "partials/en-section-free-session.twig" %}


