							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
					<div itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="card">
						<div
							class="card-header collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse16">
							{# q4 #}
							<h3 itemprop="name">How Do I Get More Traffic To My Shopify Store?</h3>
						</div>
						<div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer" id="collapse16" class="collapse">
							<div itemprop="text" class="card-body">
								<p>Every online store wants more traffic, but how can you actually make it happen? The answer involves using Shopify’s data-driven insights to your company’s advantage. However, drawing actionable findings from this information requires an expert touch. By delving into your website’s data to identify sales trends and SEO improvements, we generate the most valuable website traffic possible for your business.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>


			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{% include "assets/partials/en-form-popup.twig" with {'form_page': 'Shopify SEO (Popup)'} %}
{% endblock %}
